nodes.text: Sean Kiner is a music composer who worked on Star Wars Rebels. The eldest son of Kevin Kiner—a composer who worked on both the Rebels and Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series—he and his brother, Dean, wrote music alongide their father for the Star Wars series, and Sean Kiner himself wrote "Thrawn's Theme" for Rebels. Additionally, Sean Kiner is credited as an editor and studio personnel on the Star Wars Rebels: Season One soundtrack.
